PBOC’s Yi Calls Managed Basket ‘Best’ for Economy, Xinhua Says

-- B y   M i c h a e l   P a t t e r s o n
-- 
2011-02-13T18:02:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-13/pboc-s-yi-calls-managed-basket-best-for-economy-xinhua-says.html
People’s Bank of China Deputy
Governor  Yi Gang  said a managed floating exchange rate tied to a
basket of foreign currencies is the “best choice” for  China’s
economy , the state-run Xinhua news service reported.  Yi spoke at a research conference in Beijing today, Xinhua
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:  Michael Patterson  in  London  at 
 mpatterson10@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net  